				<div class="description ">
                	<p>When evaluating inference TCO, it’s important to look at large-scale <a href="/glossary/mixture-of-experts/" target="_blank">Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) </a>and reasoning models such as DeepSeek-R1. Nearly all of the latest closed and open source LLMs have adopted MoE and reasoning architectures, due to their superior intelligence and efficiency. By evaluating these models for inference TCO, you ensure your analysis is representative of what will likely be deployed.</p>
